description: Welcome to this stunning penthouse condo in a charming unattached brick building in the heart of South Boston! Spanning over 1,000 sq. ft., this bright & airy Eastside home is drenched in natural light & has been completely renovated. It features two spacious bedrooms with great closet space and a cozy fireplace in the master suite for those chilly nights. The master suite also offers a luxurious, newly renovated, master bath with oversized, walk-in glass enclosed shower with a rain head. The inviting living room, also with a handsome gas fireplace, seamlessly flows into the gourmet open kitchen, which boasts an eat-in area and a stylish breakfast bar. The completely renovated guest bathroom has stackable laundry as well as a soaking tub. A large walkout private deck off the living space makes entertaining or enjoying your morning coffee easy. Ideally located close East Broadway's vibrant restaurants, bars, shops as well as the beach, Castle Island & public transit.
